config MT_SND_SOC_6570
	bool "MT_SND_SOC_6570"
	default n
	help
	  If you say Y, enable MT_SND_SOC_6570_driver.
	  Must enable this to use medatek audio driver.
	  The default value is n for MT6570.
	  It is recommended not to change this.

